        "action": "Require local authorities ensure taxi ranks have raised area for accessibility",
        "additional_details": "This would help wheelchair users to use taxis safely and more easily, and help the UK to meet its goal of becoming the most accessible country in the World!",
        "background": "I want the Government to require all local authorities to make sure all taxi ranks have a raised area to allow wheelchair users and those with limited mobility to have easier and safer access to taxis.",
